column2: Integrate Korea into the honorable Japanese government, so that we may grow mighty in the worlds eyes.
Despite being the lest populated of China, Manchuria is difficult to manage. We require local support in order to pacify the countryside.
Hideki Tojo and his supporters from the Kwantung Army have gained a great deal of support, especially among the nationalists within our government.
We have a special division dedicated to administrating Manchukuo
The Headquarters of the Kwantung Army
